Laba bafundi basesikoleni samabanga aphansi iMdloti Primary eConiston, eVerulam kuthiwa bebehamba ngeNyathi ngesikhathi beshayisana neVW Polo emgwaqweni uM25 ngaphandle kwaseWaterloo izolo ekuseni. Okhulumela abezimo eziphuthumayo iReaction Unit South Africa, uMnuz Prem Balram, uthe abezimo eziphuthumayo bathintwe abashayeli abebedlula eduze kwalapho kwenzeke khona ingozi becelela abalimele usizo. “Ngesikhathi abezimo eziphuthumayo befika basize izingane ezineminyaka ephakathi kweyisithupha kuya kwengu-10 ebezinemihuzukwana ngaphambi kokuthi bazidlulisele esibhedlela Osindisweni,” kusho uBalram. Uthe kusolakala ukuthi Inyathi ebihambisa izingane izithathe eWaterloo iya esikoleni ngesikhathi ishayisana neVW Polo ebiphuma eWaterloo. Kuthiwa abashayeli balezi zimoto zombili abazange balimale.